Arduino Nano
Meanwell LRS-50-5 Power Supply
120VAC Power Lead (any generic brand will do)
HC-SR501 PIR Motion Sensor (mine are DIYMall)
MG996R Servos (two)


Vertical Servo
Pin D9
Yellow Wire

Horizontal Servo
Pin D10
Green Wire

Motion Sensor
Pin D2
Blue Wire

Red LED 
Pin D3
330 ohm resistor

Blue LED
Pin D4
330 ohm resistor

WAGO Lever Connectors from Left ---> Right
[LED GND] -- [PIR 5V] -- [Servos 5V] -- [Arduino 5V] -- [DC5V in (from PSU)]


